questions.quote: You sure they haven't gone bad? You're sure they're not very, very bad?
She never tells us anything. Ross, did you know Monica's seeing someone?
Uh-huh! Join me, won't you?! Okay, what do you say we keep one, and then just like have an option on the other one?
I know! I almost called off my wedding. Oh, who's your band?!
Well, we were walking down the street and we saw that van that you guys used for catering and we realised...
All right look, y'know, this maybe tough but come on, this is Ross! I survived college with him!
I seem to have had a slight office mishap. Could you please get the key off the back of the door for me.
No, honey you're not sick! Look, I don't love you because you're organized, I love you in spite of that.
I'm not paying for half of that! I'm only staying here until my apartment gets fixed.
Excuse me? You don't think I could get a Brian? Because I could get a Brian. Believe you me. ...I'm really not.
